:"mina","e":"of","i":"مِنَ"},{"b":"17.6","h":"26.71","c":"ٱلۡقَٰنِتِينَ","d":"l-qānitīna","e":"the devoutly obedient","i":"الۡقٰنِتِيۡنَ"}],"a":{"g":"And [the example of] Mary, the daughter of 'Imran, who guarded her chastity, so We blew into [her garment] through Our angel, and she believed in the words of her Lord and His scriptures and was of the devoutly obedient."}}}